347
00:19:28,870 --> 00:19:30,070
Do you want to try mine?

348
00:19:30,410 --> 00:19:32,109
I don't really like peaches.

349
00:19:32,110 --> 00:19:33,140
Really?

350
00:19:33,680 --> 00:19:36,509
(I don't really like peaches.)

351
