425
00:23:25,538 --> 00:23:27,838
(Joking)

426
00:23:29,438 --> 00:23:32,007
Would you like me to leave?

427
00:23:32,008 --> 00:23:33,078
No.

428
00:23:38,978 --> 00:23:40,717
She's getting on her nerves.

429
