527
00:28:01,838 --> 00:28:03,548
It certainly helps with my core strength.

528
00:28:06,018 --> 00:28:09,148
(It's a good workout that helps distract them.)

529
00:28:11,218 --> 00:28:12,318
This is good.

530
00:28:13,818 --> 00:28:17,088
(One guy is panting especially loudly.)

531
00:28:17,888 --> 00:28:20,297
(Shivering)

532
00:28:20,298 --> 00:28:21,928
These may be too light.

533
00:28:24,668 --> 00:28:26,868
Jae Seung might faint.

534
00:28:28,698 --> 00:28:32,907
(He stops before fainting.)

535
00:28:32,908 --> 00:28:34,988
Didn't you say Jae Seung was getting manual therapy?

536
00:28:37,078 --> 00:28:39,147
I heard that Jae Seung had bad knees too.

537
00:28:39,148 --> 00:28:40,247
(The patient is overworking himself.)

538
00:28:40,248 --> 00:28:42,588
We get worried when he works out.

539
00:28:43,018 --> 00:28:44,688
That's not important right now.

540
00:28:45,448 --> 00:28:47,088
The emotional wounds are too deep.

541
00:28:47,618 --> 00:28:48,818
It felt like...

542
00:28:49,028 --> 00:28:52,187
love was already out of the picture,

543
00:28:52,188 --> 00:28:53,328
so I decided to gain muscle.

544
00:28:53,698 --> 00:28:55,128
He even forgot about the pain.

545
00:28:55,968 --> 00:28:57,327
That's funny.

546
00:28:57,328 --> 00:28:59,297
(The wounded men's night draws on.)

547
00:28:59,298 --> 00:29:00,438
I pity these two.

548
00:29:01,038 --> 00:29:02,198
It's nice, though.

549
00:29:05,038 --> 00:29:07,307
(Woo Seo Yoon, Cho Eun Byul, and Shin Jae Hyuk, cocktail bar)

550
00:29:07,308 --> 00:29:08,378
They went to a bar?

551
00:29:08,438 --> 00:29:09,847
They also went to a bar.

552
00:29:09,848 --> 00:29:13,147
What do people call this place? A cocktail bar?

553
00:29:13,148 --> 00:29:14,448
- Yes.
- A cocktail bar?

554
00:29:14,578 --> 00:29:16,918
- I think so.
- Right?

555
00:29:16,948 --> 00:29:19,818
It's like a place mobsters would come to.

556
00:29:22,788 --> 00:29:24,658
- They'd put a pistol on the table.
- Right.

557
00:29:25,428 --> 00:29:27,998
They'll barge in and make a whole scene.

558
00:29:35,968 --> 00:29:39,038
What do you think of my knife skills?

559
00:29:39,578 --> 00:29:41,178
You're good.

560
00:29:43,078 --> 00:29:46,378
- Does it look even?
- Even?

561
00:29:46,548 --> 00:29:47,748
- Even?
- Not that good?

562
00:29:50,318 --> 00:29:51,618
Thanks for the food.

563
00:29:52,858 --> 00:29:55,088
Seo Yoon is proactive, isn't she?

564
00:29:55,418 --> 00:29:57,527
She just...

565
00:29:57,528 --> 00:29:58,858
She plays along well.

566
00:29:59,728 --> 00:30:00,798
It's really good.

567
00:30:01,998 --> 00:30:03,368
Is that your favorite saying?

568
00:30:03,598 --> 00:30:05,168
Did you practice it beforehand?

569
00:30:05,598 --> 00:30:07,398
No, it really is good.

570
00:30:07,768 --> 00:30:09,638
I'm only eating delicious food while I'm here.

571
00:30:10,438 --> 00:30:15,108
It also reminds me of the squid yesterday.

572
00:30:15,848 --> 00:30:17,578
- That was delicious.
- It was.

573
00:30:18,648 --> 00:30:21,918
(The two continue to talk to each other.)

574
00:30:22,118 --> 00:30:23,118
It looks like...

575
00:30:23,119 --> 00:30:24,518
- Seo Yoon is leading it.
- Yes.

576
00:30:26,018 --> 00:30:29,558
(Eun Byul can't seem to join them.)

577
00:30:33,398 --> 00:30:34,398
(Glancing)

578
00:30:36,598 --> 00:30:39,138
I don't know if I'm allowed to say this, but...

579
00:30:41,268 --> 00:30:42,338
I actually...

580
00:30:44,508 --> 00:30:47,808
enjoyed the dates with you two.

581
00:30:48,338 --> 00:30:50,378
I'm thankful for both of you.

582
00:30:51,178 --> 00:30:53,578
- I'm also thankful.
- So am I.

583
00:30:54,778 --> 00:30:56,518
I'm also thankful.

584
00:30:59,418 --> 00:31:02,218
It looks like a religious meeting.

585
00:31:03,528 --> 00:31:05,128
They're all thankful.

586
00:31:05,458 --> 00:31:07,127
- They give to each other...
- It's like...

587
00:31:07,128 --> 00:31:08,397
and accept gratitude.

588
00:31:08,398 --> 00:31:09,727
"Brothers and sisters."

589
00:31:09,728 --> 00:31:13,098
(The vibe of the date is completely different from that of Hee Dong's.)

590
00:31:13,698 --> 00:31:15,698
I was just curious.

591
00:31:17,438 --> 00:31:20,708
You picked me.

592
00:31:22,308 --> 00:31:23,348
Why...

593
00:31:24,178 --> 00:31:28,448
I wonder why you did.

594
00:31:31,218 --> 00:31:32,718
That's a tricky question.

595
00:31:32,818 --> 00:31:34,487
How will they answer genuinely?

596
00:31:34,488 --> 00:31:35,617
They might concern each others' feelings.

597
00:31:35,618 --> 00:31:37,698
(An important question to figure out their feelings)

598
00:31:38,828 --> 00:31:43,968
(Why they picked Jae Hyuk as their number-1 choice)

599
00:31:47,298 --> 00:31:48,838
- The reason?
- Yes.

600
00:31:55,108 --> 00:31:57,248
I just had...

601
00:31:58,708 --> 00:32:01,378
the most fun with you.

602
00:32:03,188 --> 00:32:05,317
That's why I picked you.

603
00:32:05,318 --> 00:32:07,018
(Seo Yoon calmly tells him her feelings.)

604
00:32:14,998 --> 00:32:17,998
I did tell you about this,

605
00:32:18,768 --> 00:32:19,798
but...

606
00:32:23,868 --> 00:32:28,208
I was absolutely tense on the first day,

607
00:32:28,878 --> 00:32:31,247
and I could start speaking...

608
00:32:31,248 --> 00:32:34,578
after the 1-on-1 date with you.

609
00:32:35,178 --> 00:32:37,917
I was able to open up to others...

610
00:32:37,918 --> 00:32:39,887
after our date.

611
00:32:39,888 --> 00:32:42,758
I felt more comfortable, thanks to you.

612
00:32:43,228 --> 00:32:44,258
Also,

613
00:32:45,688 --> 00:32:47,997
I went to a roller rink for the first time.

614
00:32:47,998 --> 00:32:51,297
And the sea squirts. I could try...

615
00:32:51,298 --> 00:32:54,738
a bunch of new things that day.

616
00:32:54,998 --> 00:32:56,668
I noticed...

617
00:32:57,608 --> 00:33:00,378
a new side of myself.

618
00:33:00,778 --> 00:33:03,608
I actually enjoy trying out new things.

619
00:33:03,978 --> 00:33:05,678
I thought...

620
00:33:06,618 --> 00:33:10,988
we were compatible in that sense.

621
00:33:11,988 --> 00:33:13,418
This is embarrassing.

622
00:33:22,968 --> 00:33:24,128
Thank you.

623
00:33:26,768 --> 00:33:27,998
She's so eloquent.

624
00:33:28,638 --> 00:33:30,108
That was pretty deep.

625
00:33:30,308 --> 00:33:31,367
She spoke slowly,

626
00:33:31,368 --> 00:33:33,168
yet she said everything that was on her mind.

627
00:33:34,038 --> 00:33:36,407
Considering her personality,

628
00:33:36,408 --> 00:33:38,177
- she wouldn't have gone that far.
- Right.

629
00:33:38,178 --> 00:33:41,047
But given the situation, she might not have been able...

630
00:33:41,048 --> 00:33:43,747
to tell him how she felt about him until the end.

631
00:33:43,748 --> 00:33:45,748
- Right.
- She could have missed the chance,

632
00:33:45,988 --> 00:33:48,588
so she confessed her honest feelings.

633
00:33:48,658 --> 00:33:52,127
I used to think Eun Byul was mature.

634
00:33:52,128 --> 00:33:53,227
But this helped me realize...

635
00:33:53,228 --> 00:33:55,497
that she was also one of the kids these days.

636
00:33:55,498 --> 00:33:57,697
She set her mind to go for him,

637
00:33:57,698 --> 00:33:59,367
so she went for him.

638
00:33:59,368 --> 00:34:01,737
- She expressed her feelings.
- She expressed her feelings.

639
00:34:01,738 --> 00:34:04,008
She knows how to do it in a polished manner.

640
00:34:04,138 --> 00:34:06,737
- So Jae Hyuk can be less flustered.
- Yes.

641
00:34:06,738 --> 00:34:08,137
Since she speaks calmly.

642
00:34:08,138 --> 00:34:10,178
(Eun Byul's feelings would've reached Jae Hyuk.)

643
00:34:11,108 --> 00:34:12,508
This is embarrassing.

644
00:34:12,878 --> 00:34:13,878
Then...

645
00:34:14,848 --> 00:34:17,647
If something new drops while we're on a date,

646
00:34:17,648 --> 00:34:19,358
do we need to say goodbye?

647
00:34:20,158 --> 00:34:21,657
Well, if that's how you think...

648
00:34:21,658 --> 00:34:23,227
I'm joking.

649
00:34:23,228 --> 00:34:26,358
There are many things I haven't experienced.

650
00:34:26,498 --> 00:34:29,228
I'd never even been to a roller rink before.

651
00:34:29,968 --> 00:34:32,568
I got to do that,

652
00:34:33,198 --> 00:34:35,338
so I really had fun.

653
00:34:41,108 --> 00:34:43,778
Eun Byul's story seems to have moved him more.

654
00:34:53,588 --> 00:34:55,657
I spoke too shortly.

655
00:34:55,658 --> 00:34:58,458
- Sorry, I spoke for too long.
- No.

656
00:35:00,598 --> 00:35:02,997
I made it short...

657
00:35:02,998 --> 00:35:06,838
because I was afraid the atmosphere would turn uncomfortable.

658
00:35:07,238 --> 00:35:10,868
Eun Byul might feel bothered too,

659
00:35:11,508 --> 00:35:15,508
so I kept it simple.

660
00:35:15,678 --> 00:35:19,148
But later, I thought I should've spoken longer.

661
00:35:19,478 --> 00:35:21,018
I regret a lot.

662
00:35:24,288 --> 00:35:26,957
(Eun Byul's genuine confession made Seo Yoon nervous.)

663
00:35:26,958 --> 00:35:28,957
Seo Yoon must've felt the shift in the air too.

664
00:35:28,958 --> 00:35:29,958
Of course.

665
00:35:29,959 --> 00:35:32,119
(Eun Byul's genuine confession made Seo Yoon nervous.)

666
00:35:39,568 --> 00:35:42,907
(The night where one shares her sincere feelings...)

667
00:35:42,908 --> 00:35:46,238
(and one is left with regrets)

668
00:35:47,438 --> 00:35:54,178
(What changes will this date bring?)

669
00:35:54,278 --> 00:35:57,748
Seo Yoon was being considerate of Eun Byul,

670
00:35:57,948 --> 00:35:59,487
so she couldn't fully express...

671
00:35:59,488 --> 00:36:01,557
her honest feelings for Jae Hyuk.

672
00:36:01,558 --> 00:36:03,858
- Exactly. This...
- Yes.

673
00:36:03,988 --> 00:36:08,858
Seo Yoon observes the situation calmly.

674
00:36:08,958 --> 00:36:10,897
She needs to take the lead,

675
00:36:10,898 --> 00:36:13,367
- but so far, she hasn't.
- Right.

676
00:36:13,368 --> 00:36:14,798
- She's hesitating.
- Yes.

677
00:36:14,998 --> 00:36:18,038
But after seeing Eun Byul express herself clearly,

678
00:36:18,368 --> 00:36:20,107
she would find the right timing...

679
00:36:20,108 --> 00:36:21,677
- to do something now.
- Yes.

680
00:36:21,678 --> 00:36:23,577
She really must step up now.

681
00:36:23,578 --> 00:36:25,607
- Exactly.
- Now's the time.

682
00:36:25,608 --> 00:36:26,947
That's how Eun Byul was initially.

683
00:36:26,948 --> 00:36:27,948
Yes.

684
00:36:28,918 --> 00:36:33,188
(While Eun Byul expresses her feelings...)

685
00:36:34,088 --> 00:36:36,257
(Jae Seung is lying down alone.)

686
00:36:36,258 --> 00:36:37,457
Jae Seung.

687
00:36:37,458 --> 00:36:39,627
Jae Seung, poor Jae Seung.

688
00:36:39,628 --> 00:36:40,958
He's by himself.

689
00:36:43,868 --> 00:36:45,998
(Jumping out of bed)

690
00:36:49,068 --> 00:36:53,138
(He suddenly gets ready to go out.)

691
00:37:03,088 --> 00:37:05,648
(He arrives at the Letter Room.)

692
00:37:06,118 --> 00:37:07,758
- Yes, Jae Seung.
- Who is he writing to?

693
00:37:08,058 --> 00:37:09,338
Isn't this his first time there?

694
00:37:09,418 --> 00:37:10,527
- You're right.
- He's going to write a letter?

695
00:37:10,528 --> 00:37:12,588
Jae Seung is mustering up his courage?

696
00:37:23,168 --> 00:37:25,208
I came up to the room...

697
00:37:25,568 --> 00:37:29,108
because I wanted to write some emotional words to Eun Byul.

698
00:37:31,408 --> 00:37:32,977
(Touched)

699
00:37:32,978 --> 00:37:34,547
Jae Seung.

700
00:37:34,548 --> 00:37:37,047
Eun Byul just did something akin to confession.

701
00:37:37,048 --> 00:37:38,217
Exactly.

702
00:37:38,218 --> 00:37:40,058
- Eun Byul left.
- Oh, dear.

703
00:37:43,488 --> 00:37:46,598
(Jae Seung is deep in thoughts.)

704
00:37:50,198 --> 00:37:55,968
(After thinking long and hard, he writes the first word.)

705
00:37:57,538 --> 00:37:58,637
(Winter)

706
00:37:58,638 --> 00:38:00,038
- "Winter." - "Winter?"

707
00:38:06,448 --> 00:38:07,648
"Love."

708
00:38:08,078 --> 00:38:09,617
He's writing a letter.

709
00:38:09,618 --> 00:38:13,517
(Love, )

710
00:38:13,518 --> 00:38:14,657
(although I can't say that word)

711
00:38:14,658 --> 00:38:16,428
"Love, although I can't say that word."

712
00:38:17,488 --> 00:38:18,887
"Although I can't say that word."

713
00:38:18,888 --> 00:38:19,958
(Hold on.)

714
00:38:20,228 --> 00:38:22,998
- Like this, from afar - Like this, from afar

715
00:38:23,598 --> 00:38:27,298
(Singing together)

716
00:38:27,468 --> 00:38:29,737
- I could give you everything - I could give you everything

717
00:38:29,738 --> 00:38:31,208
This is so sad.

718
00:38:32,468 --> 00:38:33,738
Isn't that plagiarizing?

719
00:38:34,308 --> 00:38:35,828
He just changed the title to "Winter."

720
00:38:36,038 --> 00:38:38,007
The title of this song isn't "Winter."

721
00:38:38,008 --> 00:38:39,008
It isn't.

722
00:38:39,009 --> 00:38:40,318
(Embarrassed)

723
00:38:43,018 --> 00:38:44,618
(Shaking his head)

724
00:38:45,748 --> 00:38:48,618
(In the end, he crosses out the sentence.)

725
00:38:56,898 --> 00:39:00,198
(He takes out a new piece of paper.)

726
00:39:01,098 --> 00:39:03,007
(From winter...)

727
00:39:03,008 --> 00:39:04,938
He added "night" to "winter."

728
00:39:06,478 --> 00:39:09,378
The title was "Winter Night." The content...

729
00:39:09,908 --> 00:39:12,307
("Winter Night" by Lee Jae Seung)

730
00:39:12,308 --> 00:39:14,348
"Love, although I can't say that word,"

731
00:39:15,778 --> 00:39:17,418
"on this cold day,"

732
00:39:18,588 --> 00:39:22,118
"I stand here and wait only for you."

733
00:39:27,858 --> 00:39:28,998
(Shaking his head)

734
00:39:30,728 --> 00:39:33,937
(He folds the letter written with care...)

735
00:39:33,938 --> 00:39:36,238
(and puts it in his pocket.)

736
00:39:36,538 --> 00:39:37,907
(He walks down lonelily.)

737
00:39:37,908 --> 00:39:39,167
- What?
- He put it in his pocket.

738
00:39:39,168 --> 00:39:40,277
- You can't send it?
- Is he going to...

739
00:39:40,278 --> 00:39:41,278
pass it to her himself?

740
00:39:43,948 --> 00:39:46,648
(He opens the letter again.)

741
00:39:46,878 --> 00:39:49,578
I wanted to write a poem,

742
00:39:49,788 --> 00:39:51,548
so I wrote it in the form of poetry.

743
00:39:53,818 --> 00:39:55,778
But I just couldn't get myself to send it to her,

744
00:39:56,158 --> 00:39:57,388
so I took it with me.

745
00:40:04,998 --> 00:40:06,168
(Throwing)

746
00:40:08,468 --> 00:40:10,408
Is he going to burn it?

747
00:40:16,208 --> 00:40:18,048
Goodness!

748
00:40:18,748 --> 00:40:20,548
- Poor him.
- This...

749
00:40:20,718 --> 00:40:22,048
He incinerated it?

750
00:40:22,178 --> 00:40:24,388
Poor him.

751
00:40:25,648 --> 00:40:26,818
Isn't he acting pitiful?

752
00:40:27,558 --> 00:40:29,558
(Embarrassed)

753
00:40:32,428 --> 00:40:35,828
I think Eun Byul has pretty much decided on her feelings.

754
00:40:36,468 --> 00:40:39,128
When I burned that letter,

755
00:40:39,328 --> 00:40:42,498
I took the moment to get over her too.

756
00:40:43,268 --> 00:40:45,138
Now that I see it,

757
00:40:45,168 --> 00:40:47,238
he's doing performance art.

758
00:40:48,338 --> 00:40:49,338
Performance art.

759
00:40:49,339 --> 00:40:51,248
He wrote a heartfelt letter...

760
00:40:51,408 --> 00:40:54,448
and burned it. The whole process is art.

761
00:40:56,488 --> 00:41:01,088
(The letter was a practice for a goodbye, not a confession.)

762
00:41:01,518 --> 00:41:03,288
He's making me cry.

763
00:41:04,358 --> 00:41:07,557
Jae Seung's heart must've felt like winter.

764
00:41:07,558 --> 00:41:09,098
(In the end, Sung Mi sheds a tear.)

765
00:41:10,268 --> 00:41:12,968
Life isn't that easy.

766
00:41:13,168 --> 00:41:15,637
He's doing a breakup ritual on his own.

767
00:41:15,638 --> 00:41:17,237
(Suddenly holding a breakup ritual after one date)

768
00:41:17,238 --> 00:41:18,337
- My goodness.
- I mean...

769
00:41:18,338 --> 00:41:20,637
It's okay Jae Seung, you still have time.

770
00:41:20,638 --> 00:41:22,838
There are tomorrow and the day after tomorrow, punk.

771
00:41:23,548 --> 00:41:25,147
Practice breaking up after doing something.

772
00:41:25,148 --> 00:41:26,978
- You haven't done anything.
- He...

773
00:41:27,078 --> 00:41:28,217
He didn't get to do anything.

774
00:41:28,218 --> 00:41:30,617
He said he liked someone who liked him.

775
00:41:30,618 --> 00:41:33,188
He needs to do something,

776
00:41:33,358 --> 00:41:35,618
but he's doing nothing. What's happening?

777
00:41:35,918 --> 00:41:37,458
Why are you asking me that?

778
00:41:37,728 --> 00:41:39,388
I'm very frustrated as well.

779
00:41:39,658 --> 00:41:42,297
Practice breaking up after you do something.

780
00:41:42,298 --> 00:41:43,897
- Yes.
- You did nothing.

781
00:41:43,898 --> 00:41:45,328
In this situation,

782
00:41:45,698 --> 00:41:47,437
he wouldn't give up on Eun Byul...

783
00:41:47,438 --> 00:41:50,307
and go for someone else, would he?

784
00:41:50,308 --> 00:41:51,667
I don't think so.

785
00:41:51,668 --> 00:41:53,607
He already burned his feelings.

786
00:41:53,608 --> 00:41:55,138
"I won't love anymore."

787
00:41:55,908 --> 00:41:57,448
He's even done a ritual.

788
00:41:58,508 --> 00:42:01,017
Burning that put a full stop to it all.

789
00:42:01,018 --> 00:42:02,078
(He's reached nirvana.)

790
00:42:03,448 --> 00:42:06,348
(Meanwhile, another man who is at home)

791
00:42:08,058 --> 00:42:10,087
(The person you love)

792
00:42:10,088 --> 00:42:13,158
(I hope that's me)

793
00:42:14,098 --> 00:42:21,538
(He's sublimating his pain by singing a breakup song medley.)

794
00:42:29,008 --> 00:42:30,977
(He's not in his best condition as well.)

795
00:42:30,978 --> 00:42:33,848
It must've been painful. He's very stressed.

796
00:42:41,518 --> 00:42:42,658
This is hard.

797
00:42:44,088 --> 00:42:45,488
It's hard.

798
00:42:46,728 --> 00:42:51,527
(Yoon Hoo tosses and turns with mixed feelings.)

799
00:42:51,528 --> 00:42:55,568
Actually, when we went on the date yesterday,

800
00:42:55,968 --> 00:42:58,808
I thought it was a good chance to get to know many people.

801
00:42:59,908 --> 00:43:01,408
But today,

802
00:43:03,448 --> 00:43:05,408
it kept bothering me that Yu Bin went on a date.

803
00:43:06,618 --> 00:43:08,017
That bothered me the most.

804
00:43:08,018 --> 00:43:09,224
(The depth of his feelings has changed from yesterday.)

805
00:43:09,248 --> 00:43:12,117
Actually, I did talk a bit with the others,

806
00:43:12,118 --> 00:43:13,918
but I click the best with Yu Bin.

807
00:43:14,758 --> 00:43:16,627
You made two mistakes. It's over.

808
00:43:16,628 --> 00:43:18,887
No, you should grill this properly first.

809
00:43:18,888 --> 00:43:19,928
Okay.

810
00:43:21,028 --> 00:43:23,368
We had the best chemistry.

811
00:43:24,628 --> 00:43:26,568
We call each other...

812
00:43:26,698 --> 00:43:28,938
the relationship brought together by ice cream.

813
00:43:30,568 --> 00:43:32,508
(You don't want to eat ice cream, do you?)

814
00:43:32,768 --> 00:43:33,777
(Are you going to have it?)

815
00:43:33,778 --> 00:43:35,478
(Nodding)

816
00:43:35,708 --> 00:43:39,207
(Two of them have similar tastes...)

817
00:43:39,208 --> 00:43:44,548
(and spent time of their own every evening.)

818
00:43:46,558 --> 00:43:49,718
(Before he realized, Yoon Hoo has become attached to Yu Bin.)

819
00:43:51,528 --> 00:43:52,658
Actually,

820
00:43:53,398 --> 00:43:56,927
I don't regret just focusing on Yu Bin.

821
00:43:56,928 --> 00:43:58,267
I definitely don't regret it.

822
00:43:58,268 --> 00:44:01,138
My feelings have become firm.

823
00:44:02,398 --> 00:44:04,437
"My feelings are firm toward you."

824
00:44:04,438 --> 00:44:07,278
"I like you, Yu Bin." I should just say it.

825
00:44:07,478 --> 00:44:08,708
That's all I had in mind.

826
00:44:10,408 --> 00:44:12,507
- That's right.
- Yes.

827
00:44:12,508 --> 00:44:14,047
- He's so mature.
- Yes.

828
00:44:14,048 --> 00:44:15,178
He's cool.

829
00:44:15,518 --> 00:44:16,917
He's so cool.

830
00:44:16,918 --> 00:44:18,517
He's very thoughtful.

831
00:44:18,518 --> 00:44:20,198
(Yoon Hoo's sincerity moves Yu Bin's dad.)

832
00:44:21,088 --> 00:44:23,888
(As he waits for Yu Bin to come back, )

833
00:44:24,658 --> 00:44:28,398
(he sings the song he sang for her on their date alone.)

834
00:44:29,328 --> 00:44:36,238
(I can't do anything else but that)

835
00:44:37,268 --> 00:44:41,977
(He misses someone...)

836
00:44:41,978 --> 00:44:44,408
(and he lets go of someone.)

837
00:44:46,378 --> 00:44:52,248
(The night is filled with waiting.)

838
00:44:55,458 --> 00:44:58,327
(Park Si Woo, Choi Yu Bin, and Yoo Hee Dong at at LP bar)

839
00:44:58,328 --> 00:45:01,258
Now that we dropped the honorifics, I can clearly tell your age.

840
00:45:01,358 --> 00:45:02,398
Me too.

841
00:45:03,268 --> 00:45:04,968
- I felt it so clearly.
- Okay.

842
00:45:06,528 --> 00:45:08,667
It really feels like we're the same age.

843
00:45:08,668 --> 00:45:09,698
Yes.

844
00:45:09,968 --> 00:45:11,837
It could be because we're speaking casually now.

845
00:45:11,838 --> 00:45:14,198
(Even now, only Yu Bin and Hee Dong are speaking casually.)

846
00:45:18,378 --> 00:45:20,017
Isn't it better than being uncomfortable?

847
00:45:20,018 --> 00:45:22,718
- I prefer speaking casually.
- Me too.

848
00:45:23,388 --> 00:45:25,847
- I prefer speaking casually.
- Me too.

849
00:45:25,848 --> 00:45:26,918
(Glancing)

850
00:45:28,218 --> 00:45:30,188
Fine. Speak casually.

851
00:45:31,288 --> 00:45:32,388
I did it.

852
00:45:32,828 --> 00:45:34,548
I wondered how longer you'd speak formally.

853
00:45:35,628 --> 00:45:37,528
- Finally.
- She agreed.

854
00:45:37,868 --> 00:45:39,928
Hee Dong must've wanted this.

855
00:45:40,168 --> 00:45:42,837
- And she should compromise.
- Yes.

856
00:45:42,838 --> 00:45:44,244
- She changed her pace.
- Not too... Yes.

857
00:45:44,268 --> 00:45:45,638
They should compromise.

858
00:45:47,808 --> 00:45:50,378
- Would you like more bread?
- Give me one more shrimp.

859
00:45:53,718 --> 00:45:54,818
- Thank you.
- One.

860
00:45:57,248 --> 00:45:59,448
- Bread?
- What? No, it's okay.

861
00:45:59,918 --> 00:46:01,857
- Do you want it?
- Here.

862
00:46:01,858 --> 00:46:02,888
Thank you.

863
00:46:03,788 --> 00:46:04,827
They're speaking comfortably now...

864
00:46:04,828 --> 00:46:05,857
- after dropping the honorifics.
- Exactly.

865
00:46:05,858 --> 00:46:08,128
They look a lot closer.

866
00:46:09,428 --> 00:46:10,728
Which high school did you go to?

867
00:46:12,268 --> 00:46:14,838
Seoul Arts High School?

868
00:46:14,968 --> 00:46:16,038
- No.
- No?

869
00:46:16,368 --> 00:46:17,608
I don't dance.

870
00:46:18,538 --> 00:46:20,277
You're definitely a dancer.

871
00:46:20,278 --> 00:46:21,438
Why do you think so?

872
00:46:22,238 --> 00:46:23,608
You just look like one.

873
00:46:24,578 --> 00:46:25,908
I have a knack for it.

874
00:46:26,308 --> 00:46:27,518
I'll tell you next time.

875
00:46:31,048 --> 00:46:32,624
Did you go to sleep right away yesterday?

876
00:46:32,648 --> 00:46:34,258
- After I went back, - Yes.

877
00:46:34,658 --> 00:46:36,057
I think I went to sleep right after washing my face...

878
00:46:36,058 --> 00:46:37,088
and brushing my teeth.

879
00:46:40,028 --> 00:46:41,157
Did you go to sleep right away?

880
00:46:41,158 --> 00:46:42,958
I cleaned up first,

881
00:46:43,468 --> 00:46:45,898
and when I was done with it, it was around 3am, I think?

882
00:46:48,838 --> 00:46:53,608
(Yu Bin is left out of the conversation.)

883
00:46:55,238 --> 00:46:56,878
I didn't know it flew so fast.

884
00:46:56,948 --> 00:46:57,948
- Time?
- Yes.

885
00:46:57,948 --> 00:46:58,948
Me too.

886
00:47:00,618 --> 00:47:03,098
You acted like you'd go upstairs to write something yesterday.

887
00:47:03,218 --> 00:47:04,848
So I went up because I got curious.

888
00:47:06,218 --> 00:47:09,018
- You thought I'd write something?
- Yes, I thought you'd write again.

889
00:47:10,088 --> 00:47:11,328
You were looking forward to it.

890
00:47:12,288 --> 00:47:13,498
I'll write one today.

891
00:47:15,928 --> 00:47:18,228
(Smiling)

892
00:47:22,598 --> 00:47:24,667
Don't all the girls know?

893
00:47:24,668 --> 00:47:27,138
I felt that Si Woo became very shy...

894
00:47:27,308 --> 00:47:30,348
in front of the guy she has feelings for.

895
00:47:31,678 --> 00:47:36,178
And Hee Dong showed so much romantic interest toward Si Woo.

896
00:47:36,548 --> 00:47:39,388
I felt that tension in the air.

897
00:47:40,588 --> 00:47:42,958
When I spoke with Hee Dong,

898
00:47:43,258 --> 00:47:47,498
it felt more or less friendly.

899
00:47:47,798 --> 00:47:50,227
Rather, the date I had with Hoo...

900
00:47:50,228 --> 00:47:53,168
made my heart flutter.

901
00:47:54,268 --> 00:47:58,208
(How can I sleep when I'm with such a beauty?)

902
00:47:59,368 --> 00:48:01,538
(I'll protect you.)

903
00:48:02,238 --> 00:48:07,848
(The date with Yoon Hoo made her heart flutter.)

904
00:48:08,078 --> 00:48:12,448
I'd have enjoyed it more if I came here with Hoo.

905
00:48:12,848 --> 00:48:15,287
And even as I ate,

906
00:48:15,288 --> 00:48:17,627
"If I'd chosen Hoo as my first choice,"

907
00:48:17,628 --> 00:48:19,528
"what kind of date would we be having now?"

908
00:48:19,788 --> 00:48:21,128
I had that thought.

909
00:48:23,768 --> 00:48:25,267
She didn't forget Hoo.

910
00:48:25,268 --> 00:48:27,267
(Yu Bin kept thinking about Hoo.)

911
00:48:27,268 --> 00:48:30,537
I told you. Now that they're apart...

912
00:48:30,538 --> 00:48:31,538
- Yes.
- That's right.

913
00:48:31,539 --> 00:48:33,507
- That's how they become solid.
- You need a moment like this too.

914
00:48:33,508 --> 00:48:35,507
- Yes.
- Today...

915
00:48:35,508 --> 00:48:37,978
made Hoo and Yu Bin grow closer.

916
00:48:38,178 --> 00:48:39,178
Yes.

917
00:48:39,179 --> 00:48:40,277
It's an important turning point...

918
00:48:40,278 --> 00:48:41,347
- for them.
- Let us...

919
00:48:41,348 --> 00:48:42,778
get along well.

920
00:48:43,048 --> 00:48:44,187
My goodness.

921
00:48:44,188 --> 00:48:46,087
- I'm sorry.
- "I'm sorry."

922
00:48:46,088 --> 00:48:47,488
It's okay, same here.

923
00:48:52,788 --> 00:48:54,127
I'll take a nap.

924
00:48:54,128 --> 00:48:56,798
You two go ahead and talk.

925
00:49:00,838 --> 00:49:03,508
(Tossing around)

926
00:49:04,708 --> 00:49:07,078
They didn't have the chance to talk by themselves...

927
00:49:08,178 --> 00:49:09,808
because of me.

928
00:49:10,178 --> 00:49:12,608
So I told them to talk...

929
00:49:12,748 --> 00:49:14,448
and pretended to sleep.

930
00:49:15,378 --> 00:49:16,617
(Proud of her)

931
00:49:16,618 --> 00:49:19,548
Yu Bin supports them.

932
00:49:20,518 --> 00:49:22,688
You're so witty. That's my daughter.

933
00:49:23,288 --> 00:49:24,987
- They're by themselves now.
- Yes.

934
00:49:24,988 --> 00:49:27,628
(Si Woo and Hee Dong have the time of their own thanks to Yu Bin.)

935
00:49:30,058 --> 00:49:33,368
(They keep giggling from just looking at each other.)

936
00:49:35,738 --> 00:49:39,108
Do you normally not approach others first?

937
00:49:40,878 --> 00:49:42,878
I've never approached.

938
00:49:45,378 --> 00:49:46,378
Me neither.

939
00:49:46,379 --> 00:49:47,448
- Really?
- Yes.

940
00:49:48,818 --> 00:49:49,878
I'm serious.

941
00:49:50,388 --> 00:49:52,418
Then the others always approached you first?

942
00:49:53,148 --> 00:49:54,418
Normally, yes.

943
00:49:57,758 --> 00:49:59,557
Were you always on the receiving end...

944
00:49:59,558 --> 00:50:00,597
- of confessions?
- Me?

945
00:50:00,598 --> 00:50:01,658
Yes.

946
00:50:02,728 --> 00:50:04,098
But I always...

947
00:50:05,428 --> 00:50:06,938
liked the other person first.

948
00:50:08,238 --> 00:50:10,168
But I didn't say it.

949
00:50:10,838 --> 00:50:12,368
I just liked them.

950
00:50:14,778 --> 00:50:16,808
(Hesitating)

951
00:50:17,748 --> 00:50:18,848
But...

952
00:50:20,448 --> 00:50:21,778
I'll be very honest.

953
00:50:23,818 --> 00:50:26,088
I tried my best for you in my own way.

954
00:50:27,658 --> 00:50:28,688
I see.

955
00:50:30,858 --> 00:50:32,828
(Feeling shy)

956
00:50:33,158 --> 00:50:34,428
You know,

957
00:50:36,098 --> 00:50:37,898
I felt that too.

958
00:50:38,398 --> 00:50:39,468
But...

959
00:50:41,198 --> 00:50:44,108
I feel shy to express it.

960
00:50:46,268 --> 00:50:47,708
Why does it make you feel shy?

961
00:50:49,508 --> 00:50:50,708
Why does it make you feel shy?

962
00:50:53,478 --> 00:50:54,917
Hee Dong, what will you reply?

963
00:50:54,918 --> 00:50:56,377
- Hee Dong.
- Why does it make him feel shy?

964
00:50:56,378 --> 00:50:57,787
Say it and she'll fall over.

965
00:50:57,788 --> 00:50:58,817
Yes.

966
00:50:58,818 --> 00:51:00,118
(Hee Dong's reply is important.)

967
00:51:01,058 --> 00:51:04,487
It seems that I tend to speak less when I'm with someone I like.

968
00:51:04,488 --> 00:51:08,097
(It seems that I tend to speak less when I'm with someone I like.)

969
00:51:08,098 --> 00:51:09,298
Same goes for me.

970
00:51:12,728 --> 00:51:13,738
Si Woo.

971
00:51:14,038 --> 00:51:16,137
- She must feel relieved now.
- She's smiling.

972
00:51:16,138 --> 00:51:17,138
(Sighing in relief)

973
00:51:18,108 --> 00:51:19,708
Honestly speaking...

974
00:51:23,178 --> 00:51:25,748
(Hesitating)

975
00:51:32,188 --> 00:51:33,717
It's a shame we couldn't go together.

976
00:51:33,718 --> 00:51:36,888
(It's a shame we couldn't go on a date together.)

977
00:51:41,858 --> 00:51:43,927
(Although Hee Dong feels shy, )

978
00:51:43,928 --> 00:51:47,198
(he musters up the courage and expresses his feelings.)

979
00:51:52,638 --> 00:51:56,477
(Hee Dong finally shows his true feelings.)

980
00:51:56,478 --> 00:51:59,278
Didn't he practically confess?

981
00:51:59,478 --> 00:52:02,148
Hee Dong had Si Woo on his mind.

982
00:52:02,578 --> 00:52:04,648
I'm a bit moved.

983
00:52:04,718 --> 00:52:07,157
But Yu Bin is listening in front.

984
00:52:07,158 --> 00:52:08,357
She's only pretending to sleep.

985
00:52:08,358 --> 00:52:11,658
She's blocking them out, considering everything.

986
00:52:17,968 --> 00:52:19,027
- She really slept.
- Did she really sleep?

987
00:52:19,028 --> 00:52:20,467
- She said she'd pretend to sleep.
- She must've really slept.

988
00:52:20,468 --> 00:52:22,137
- She really slept.
- She really slept.

989
00:52:22,138 --> 00:52:23,338
She didn't pretend to.

990
00:52:23,668 --> 00:52:25,438
You can sleep longer.

991
00:52:27,578 --> 00:52:32,208
(Yu Bin pretends to sleep again.)

992
00:52:32,878 --> 00:52:34,977
(Yu Bin, the queen of consideration)

993
00:52:34,978 --> 00:52:36,148
Yu Bin.

994
00:52:36,248 --> 00:52:38,917
That's right, sleep more. Good job.

995
00:52:38,918 --> 00:52:40,818
(Good job, my daughter.)

996
00:52:41,058 --> 00:52:42,987
(With a sweet nap, 8 of them all return.)

997
00:52:42,988 --> 00:52:44,028
We're back.

998
00:52:45,988 --> 00:52:48,098
- You're back.
- Where's Hoo?

999
00:52:48,798 --> 00:52:50,898
- He's asleep.
- Really?

1000
00:52:52,628 --> 00:52:53,967
(Upon returning, Yu Bin looks for Hoo first.)

1001
00:52:53,968 --> 00:52:55,448
- She's looking for Hoo first.
- Yes.

1002
00:52:56,638 --> 00:52:58,438
Is he not eating jjajang ramyeon?

1003
00:52:59,108 --> 00:53:00,607
He probably will.

1004
00:53:00,608 --> 00:53:01,907
I asked to eat together,

1005
00:53:01,908 --> 00:53:03,278
but he said he'd wait for you.

1006
00:53:06,648 --> 00:53:09,518
(Pondering)

1007
00:53:11,848 --> 00:53:15,658
(After thinking hard, Yu Bin gets up from her seat.)

1008
00:53:22,628 --> 00:53:24,228
Hoo is asleep.

1009
00:53:26,168 --> 00:53:27,968
- Really?
- What should I do?

1010
00:53:28,698 --> 00:53:29,938
Is it bad if I wake him up?

1011
00:53:30,468 --> 00:53:32,437
- Shouldn't you wake him up, though?
- Exactly.

1012
00:53:32,438 --> 00:53:36,638
(Yu Bin is worried about Yoon Hoo's feelings.)

1013
00:53:41,978 --> 00:53:43,148
I'm off.

1014
00:53:43,578 --> 00:53:44,648
You're going?

1015
00:53:45,348 --> 00:53:46,447
- Really?
- Yes.

1016
00:53:46,448 --> 00:53:48,058
Good luck.

1017
00:53:51,928 --> 00:53:53,387
- She's going to Hoo.
- Yes.

1018
00:53:53,388 --> 00:53:54,797
Yes, go and see Hoo.

1019
00:53:54,798 --> 00:53:56,998
(With Si Woo cheering her on, Yu Bin goes to Yoon Hoo.)

1020
00:53:58,968 --> 00:54:00,028
Hoo.

1021
00:54:01,438 --> 00:54:02,468
Are you asleep?

1022
00:54:05,708 --> 00:54:07,008
Hoo, are you asleep?

1023
00:54:08,508 --> 00:54:12,378
(But Hoo is sleeping deeply.)

1024
00:54:13,648 --> 00:54:14,677
He sleeps deeply.

1025
00:54:14,678 --> 00:54:18,118
(He feels bad.)

1026
00:54:18,788 --> 00:54:21,157
(A bit later)

1027
00:54:21,158 --> 00:54:22,188
He's awake.

1028
00:54:24,228 --> 00:54:25,627
- Hello.
- Hello.

1029
00:54:25,628 --> 00:54:27,728
(Hoo finally wakes up.)

1030
00:54:29,498 --> 00:54:31,498
- Hello.
- Hello.

1031
00:54:32,028 --> 00:54:34,798
- It looks like you slept well.
- That's right.

1032
00:54:37,508 --> 00:54:42,708
(Things are still awkward between Hoo and Yu Bin.)

1033
00:54:46,448 --> 00:54:49,548
(At that moment, they receive a mysterious text.)

1034
00:54:50,318 --> 00:54:56,517
(Please reveal your age and profession now.)

1035
00:54:56,518 --> 00:55:00,087
"Please reveal your age and profession now."

1036
00:55:00,088 --> 00:55:01,957
- Finally.
- Finally.

1037
00:55:01,958 --> 00:55:03,097
Finally.

1038
00:55:03,098 --> 00:55:04,267
Whom they're attracted to might change.

1039
00:55:04,268 --> 00:55:05,828
- It might change.
- That's right.

1040
00:55:07,438 --> 00:55:09,068
Now that we need to do it...

1041
00:55:09,398 --> 00:55:10,808
- I know.
- It's a bit...

1042
00:55:11,238 --> 00:55:13,737
- We've been waiting for this.
- Seriously.

1043
00:55:13,738 --> 00:55:15,014
(The information that might change the flow will be revealed.)

1044
00:55:15,038 --> 00:55:17,607
To be honest, I was so curious...

1045
00:55:17,608 --> 00:55:19,348
about everyone's age.

1046
00:55:19,978 --> 00:55:22,517
I prefer an older man...

1047
00:55:22,518 --> 00:55:24,848
for mature personality.

1048
00:55:25,388 --> 00:55:28,557
I'm interested in something...

1049
00:55:28,558 --> 00:55:29,887
who leads me.

1050
00:55:29,888 --> 00:55:32,188
That's why I prefer an older man.

1051
00:55:33,388 --> 00:55:35,257
Why am I nervous about this?

1052
00:55:35,258 --> 00:55:36,298
Seriously.

1053
00:55:37,128 --> 00:55:38,397
We're nervous as well.

1054
00:55:38,398 --> 00:55:42,998
